title: Martha I. Warneke
maintext: JUDITH GAP — Martha I. Warneke, 77, of Judith Gap, died Saturday, Feb. 4, 2017. Per Martha’s request there will be no services and cremation has taken place. The Cloyd Funeral Home is assisting the family.
